165
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,720
I didn't!

166
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:57,680
Grandmother.

167
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,270
Alright, alright, alright!

168
00:07:59,270 --> 00:07:59,950
Tang

169
