the Imperial Court of Judicial Review!

290
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,150
Do you really think

291
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,530
that no one in the Gu Mansion

292
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,700
can do anything about you?

293
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:31,870
Someone!

294
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:33,440
Yes!

295
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:35,870
Lock her in the wood shed.

296
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:36,720
Do not let her out

297
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,440
without my orders!

298
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:37,960
Yes!

299
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,670
Who dares!

300
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,200
Old Madam,

301
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:33,550
Second Young Master of the Ji family
is here.

302
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:35,350
with over a dozen carts of gifts,

303
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:37,630
saying he's here to propose marriage.

304
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:38,270
He wants

305
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,080
to marry Miss Gu.

306
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,810
It's just a marriage proposal.

307
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:44,970
What's the big deal?

308
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:47,360
Just because someone is here to propose,

309
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:49,420
I can't punish my own granddaughter?

310
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,320
Do it.

311
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:52,750
Old Madam,

312
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:56,220
the Ji family is the subordinate
of the Chen family.

313
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:01,630
Fine.

314
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:05,240
Have Young Master Ji wait
in the front hall.

315
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:06,870
I'll go right now.

316
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:07,630
Yes.

317
00:14:10,970 --> 00:14:12,900
Are my second and fourth sons back?

318
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,360
Only Fourth Master
is off duty

319
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,270
and just back.

320
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,230
Ask him to go too.

321
00:14:17,230 --> 00:14:17,830
Yes.

322
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:20,870
Go now.

323
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,030
Did you ask Young Master Ji

324
00:14:30,030 --> 00:14:30,960
to come?

325
00:14:31,550 --> 00:14:32,270
No.

326
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:35,290
Then Chen Yanyun asked him to come?

327
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,390
Of course not.

328
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:42,600
My Lady.

329
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:46,380
Second Master came to propose to you!

330
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:47,750
I don't know what's going on either.

331
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:48,120
Let's go.

332
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:50,450
Let's go around to the back
and take a look.

333
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:52,120
I pay my respects to Old Madam,

334
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,980
Second Madam, and Fourth Master.

335
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,690
Second Young Master Ji.

336
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:02,150
You want to marry Zhao?

337
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,200
Yes.

338
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:05,870
This is the betrothal gift list

339
00:15:05,870 --> 00:15:07,390
personally drafted by my grandmother.

340
00:15:07,390 --> 00:15:08,270
Please look it over,

341
00:15:08,270 --> 00:15:09,870
Old Madam and Fourth Master.

342
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:16,340
[Gu]

343
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:24,880
[A western glass mirror]
[Two thousand taels of gold]

344
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:26,120
Two thousand taels of gold.

345
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,920
Fifty thousand taels of silver.

346
00:15:31,150 --> 00:15:32,670
Mother, Mother.

347
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,080
We can talk.

348
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:43,790
We can talk.

349
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,550
I have also prepared some small gifts

350
00:15:47,550 --> 00:15:48,750
for the elders.

351
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:50,220
Please do accept them.

352
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:57,270
Old Madam,

353
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,750
I got this jade bracelet

354
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:01,510
when I followed the grain boats
to Taungoo.

355
00:16:01,510 --> 00:16:02,790
Wear it in winter for warmth,

356
00:16:02,790 --> 00:16:04,120
in summer for coolness.

357
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:13,720
Young Master Ji,

358
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:16,010
you've been too generous.

359
00:16:17,030 --> 00:16:18,000
Coming from so far away,

360
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,260
you must be exhausted.

361
00:16:19,910 --> 00:16:20,600
Someone!

362
00:16:22,510 --> 00:16:23,110
Old Madam.

363
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:25,540
Help Young Master Ji freshen up.

364
00:16:25,670 --> 00:16:26,360
Afterward,

365
00:16:26,550 --> 00:16:28,480
escort him to the main hall to dine.

366
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:29,840
Yes.

367
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:32,750
Thank you, Old Madam.

368
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:34,680
Young Master Ji,

369
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:35,870
this way, please.

370
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:46,720
Well...

371
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,960
You are bold enough to come and propose,

372
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,090
but too shy to see me?

373
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:53,550
Not everyone is like you,

374
00:16:53,550 --> 00:16:54,810
no sense of shame,

375
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:56,670
no ability to protect yourself.

376
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,420
You caused such a big stir.

377
00:16:58,870 --> 00:16:59,670
Grandmother hasn't slept well

378
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:01,070
for days because of that.

379
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:02,630
So...

380
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:05,430
Did Grandmother ask you to come?

381
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,030
No.

382
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,720
Grandmother didn't mention it.

383
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:10,510
I came on my own.

384
00:17:12,589 --> 00:17:13,349
I heard those

385
00:17:13,349 --> 00:17:14,609
nasty words about you.

386
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:16,730
Those are all rumors.

387
00:17:17,069 --> 00:17:18,550
I know they are rumors.

388
00:17:19,069 --> 00:17:20,530
But gossip is terrifying.

389
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,790
A man can barely withstand it,

390
00:17:22,790 --> 00:17:24,520
let alone a young lady like you.

391
00:17:24,829 --> 00:17:26,240
I just hate seeing people

392
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:27,920
talk nonsense and slander you.

393
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:30,160
That doesn't mean you need to
come propose.

394
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:32,240
Proposing is the best solution.

395
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:34,030
I inquired.

396
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:35,310
That Wang Zan

397
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:37,050
is a notorious scoundrel.

398
00:17:37,310 --> 00:17:38,200
Who knows what trouble

399
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,550
he'll cause later.

400
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:42,160
Rather than guarding against others
spreading rumors,

401
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:42,820
it's better

402
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:44,450
for me to propose to you now.

403
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,880
If anyone dares to trouble you
in the future,

404
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:48,000
I can rightfully

405
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,530
settle the score with them.

406
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:50,680
My lady,

407
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:54,070
the young master arrived in the capital
at noon yesterday.

408
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,960
He was supposed to meet some guests.

409
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:56,960
But when he heard

410
00:17:57,070 --> 00:17:58,330
that you were bullied,

411
00:17:58,350 --> 00:17:59,440
he was extremely worried.

412
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:00,590
He canceled his meetings

413
00:18:00,590 --> 00:18:02,510
and immediately returned to Tongzhou
to prepare.

414
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:03,400
Old Madam said

415
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:05,310
the weather was bad
and he should wait a few days.

416
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:06,510
But he couldn't wait,

417
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:08,500
insisting on rushing here today.

418
00:18:08,750 --> 00:18:10,310
He was afraid you'd be wronged.

419
00:18:10,310 --> 00:18:12,510
He didn't even have time to drink water,

420
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,720
and got blisters all over his mouth
from anxiety.

421
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:15,400
Stop it.

422
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:17,160
You are so talkative.

423
00:18:18,070 --> 00:18:19,470
Let's go to my courtyard.

424
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:21,240
I'll make you some lotus seed soup.

425
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,030
How can I?

426
00:18:22,510 --> 00:18:23,880
Now that I've proposed,

427
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:26,070
it's already inappropriate for us
to meet like this.

428
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:27,730
How can I go to your courtyard?

429
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:31,200
You should go back now.

430
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:32,510
Don't worry about anything.

431
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:33,750
Don't meddle in anything.

432
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:35,160
Leave the rest to me.

433
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:38,680
You may leave first.

434
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:40,400
Yes.

435
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,800
How could you be so willful?

436
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:46,550
This...

437
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:47,550
Yao.

438
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,160
I am truly touched

439
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:51,840
by what you're doing.

440
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,590
But do you

441
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:56,000
really like me?

442
00:19:00,350 --> 00:19:01,030
I...

443
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,550
Of course I like you.

444
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,270
Like a brother

445
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,750
likes a sister?

446
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,830
Or like the "fair lady is a gentleman's
good catch"

447
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:11,160
kind of liking?

448
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:19,310
If I am to marry someone,

449
00:19:19,570 --> 00:19:21,000
I will definitely marry a man

450
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,000
who truly loves me

451
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:23,490
and whom I truly love.

452
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,000
Furthermore,

453
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:27,070
just a little bit of liking is not enough.

454
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:28,200
It has to be the kind where

455
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:29,200
the thought of him

456
00:19:29,550 --> 00:19:31,280
keeps me awake all night,

457
00:19:32,070 --> 00:19:34,470
tossing and turning while thinking of him.

458
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:36,000
Thinking of him

459
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:37,580
would make my face burn.

460
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:39,640
That's the kind of liking it has to be.

461
00:19:49,740 --> 00:19:50,660
Yao.

462
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:53,510
We grew up together.

463
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:54,790
I also hope

464
00:19:54,910 --> 00:19:55,920
you can find a woman

465
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:57,070
you truly yearn for.

466
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:58,860
You two can get married,

467
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:01,040
and she can be my sister-in-law.

468
00:20:05,510 --> 00:20:06,790
It's getting late.

469
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,510
Go back and rest early.

470
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,750
I'll have someone make lotus seed soup

471
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,000
and bring it to you.

472
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:15,020
I'll take my leave.

473
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:26,640
"Keeps me awake all night."

474
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:30,170
"Tossing and turning
while thinking of him."

475
00:20:30,350 --> 00:20:32,400
"Making my face burn."

476
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,970
How does she know it so well?

477
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:54,240
Third Master.

478
00:20:54,590 --> 00:20:56,240
Daxing Granary has a problem.

479
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:56,750
Look.

480
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:03,730
[I risk my life to secretly report]

481
00:21:03,730 --> 00:21:04,130
[While loading relief grain
at Daxing Granary the other day...]

482
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:05,050
[I was shocked to find that the 12 million
kilograms of grain intended for Pingyang]

483
00:21:05,080 --> 00:21:06,010
[had been completely replaced with bran.
Not a single grain of rice was seen]

484
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:08,720
Bran?

485
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:13,440
I can't believe they came up with this.

486
00:21:13,790 --> 00:21:15,320
Make a trip there yourself.

487
00:21:15,510 --> 00:21:16,030
No.

488
00:21:17,590 --> 00:21:18,920
Bring the granary manager here.

489
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,580
I want to question him myself.

490
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:21,400
Yes.

491
00:21:29,110 --> 00:21:30,590
Originally, it was all rice.

492
00:21:30,590 --> 00:21:32,750
Half a month ago, it was changed to bran.

493
00:21:32,750 --> 00:21:33,720
The morning the day before yesterday,
they said

494
00:21:33,650 --> 00:21:38,180
[Immersed in the Classics and History]

495
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:36,030
it was to be sent to Pingyang
for disaster relief.

496
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:37,920
I also felt something was wrong.

497
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:40,680
There is clearly rice in the granary.

498
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:42,270
Why use bran for disaster relief?

499
00:21:42,270 --> 00:21:43,440
But I saw that their

500
00:21:43,510 --> 00:21:45,030
transport documents were all in order,

501
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:46,310
so I didn't investigate further.

502
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:47,510
Who is the Secretary

503
00:21:47,550 --> 00:21:48,960
in charge of this granary?

504
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:49,510
My Lord,

505
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,110
it's Lord Sun Shitao.

506
00:21:51,590 --> 00:21:52,680
Sun Shitao？

507
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:54,310
Third Master.

508
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:55,920
This Sun Shitao

509
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:57,590
hasn't shown up for days.

510
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,640
Then whose orders have you been following

511
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:02,100
for the grain movements
these past two days?

512
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:04,350
My Lord, look.

513
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,790
[Gu Dezhao]

514
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:25,460
[Immersed in the Classics and History]

515
00:22:48,790 --> 00:22:50,250
Greetings, Third Master.

516
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:51,620
Have a seat.

517
00:22:52,830 --> 00:22:54,230
Has something happened?

518
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:56,360
Why did you have Mr. Jiang

519
00:22:56,510 --> 00:22:58,110
bring me here secretly?

520
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,190
No rush.

521
00:23:00,030 --> 00:23:01,760
Sit down and we can talk slowly.

522
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:07,960
No one in your family noticed, right?

523
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,570
I had Qingpu keep watch.

524
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:12,000
No one will notice.

525
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:17,800
Here you are.

526
00:23:19,160 --> 00:23:20,160
Have some tea

527
00:23:20,510 --> 00:23:21,640
to calm your nerves.

528
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:24,000
Has something major happened?

529
00:23:24,270 --> 00:23:25,030
Otherwise,

530
00:23:25,310 --> 00:23:27,200
you wouldn't have asked me to come.

531
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:28,660
No matter how urgent it is,

532
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:29,680
we shouldn't talk about business

533
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:30,740
the moment we meet.

534
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:32,110
What would be

535
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:35,580
the difference from being at
the Wenyuan Pavilion?

536
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:38,680
I heard

537
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:40,240
Ji Yao proposed to you.

538
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:41,750
I didn't agree.

539
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:49,990
Oh right,

540
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:55,510
after you gave it to me last time,

541
00:23:56,510 --> 00:23:58,000
I thought it was pretty good.

542
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,260
I specially found some

543
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:00,830
for you to try.

544
00:24:09,830 --> 00:24:10,360
How is it?

545
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:11,700
Does it taste the same?

546
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:13,650
It's delicious.

547
00:24:16,090 --> 00:24:18,150
Alright, let's get down to business.

548
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:20,350
There's a severe drought in Pingyang.

549
00:24:20,350 --> 00:24:22,550
The Ministry of Revenue has authorized

550
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:25,030
12 million kilograms of relief grains.

551
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:26,590
But someone sabotaged

552
00:24:27,070 --> 00:24:28,870
and replaced the rice with bran.

553
00:24:32,590 --> 00:24:34,110
I am in charge of the Ministry of Revenue.

554
00:24:34,110 --> 00:24:34,960
And this happened

555
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:36,700
right under my nose.

556
00:24:37,030 --> 00:24:37,920
Obviously,

557
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:40,640
they want me to take the blame for this.

558
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:42,590
But they are afraid I won't be willing.

559
00:24:42,590 --> 00:24:43,830
So I am being watched.

560
00:24:44,310 --> 00:24:45,110
So,

561
00:24:45,550 --> 00:24:47,310
apologies for the unorthodox meeting

562
00:24:47,310 --> 00:24:48,270
this time.

563
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:51,880
My father

564
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:54,750
is a Director of the Treasury
in the Ministry of Revenue,

565
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:56,610
He is in charge of Daxing Granary.

566
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:57,440
Could it be

567
00:24:57,720 --> 00:24:58,350
him?

568
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,140
He is also kept in the dark.

569
00:25:01,110 --> 00:25:02,680
Someone forged his seal.

570
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,200
Who?

571
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:06,290
Your father's colleague,

572
00:25:06,550 --> 00:25:07,400
Sun Shitao.

573
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:09,400
This person is Wang Xuanfan's

574
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:10,920
old subordinate planted
in the Ministry of Revenue.

575
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,200
He's disappeared now,

576
00:25:12,500 --> 00:25:14,500
but I've sent people to look for him.

577
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:16,830
Wang Xuanfan.

578
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,230
Why did he do this?

579
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:20,880
To bring down Fan Chuan.

580
00:25:21,750 --> 00:25:23,440
Zhao Jichang, the Provincial Administration
Commissioner of Shanxi,

581
