611
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:19,240
No wonder

612
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:22,160
you already knew you were being tailed,

613
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:23,720
but couldn't make a move

614
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,850
