The relief grain

622
00:26:38,830 --> 00:26:40,430
was just sent out yesterday.

623
00:26:40,550 --> 00:26:42,010
Can it still be retrieved?

624
00:26:46,070 --> 00:26:46,800
Most likely,

625
00:26:47,590 --> 00:26:48,590
