What should we do?

630
00:26:58,050 --> 00:26:59,480
You don't need to worry too much.

631
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:01,750
I've already figured out a countermeasure.

632
00:27:01,750 --> 00:27:03,880
It will take about seven days

633
