The disaster victims must receive relief.

683
00:28:40,070 --> 00:28:41,830
That is the foundation of everything.

684
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:43,630
Once there is a riot in Pingyang,

685
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:44,750
both of us,

686
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:47,750
