699
00:29:15,730 --> 00:29:16,990
300,000 kilograms...

700
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:20,440
300,000 kilograms is still not enough.

701
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:22,160
You must go to Shaanxi, Henan,

702
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:23,830
and Jiangnan.

703
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:27,040
Even if it costs extra money,

704
00:29:27,070 --> 00:29:27,930
