Third Mr. Chen, let me ask you.

727
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,920
Where is the grain?

728
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:17,210
Where is it?

729
00:30:17,790 --> 00:30:18,480
Lord Fan.

730
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,350
Lord Fan.

731
00:30:19,550 --> 00:30:20,310
Lord Fan.

732
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:22,040
What's the need for this?

733
00:30:22,590 --> 00:30:24,270
The Grand Secretary is not here today.

734
00:30:24,270 --> 00:30:25,070
Please just calm down.

735
00:30:25,070 --> 00:30:26,460
Please calm down.

736
