797
00:33:12,510 --> 00:33:14,440
The Court's 12 million kilograms of
relief grain

798
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:16,030
ended up being bran.

799
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:18,720
Commander Ye.

800
00:33:19,310 --> 00:33:20,310
I remember your older sister

801
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:21,000
married into

802
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:22,660
the Gu family of Daxin, right?

803
00:33:23,110 --> 00:33:23,880
Perhaps you could

804
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:25,680
