806
00:33:31,790 --> 00:33:32,510
No problem.

807
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:36,590
Not only

808
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:38,850
Gu Dezhao, the Director of the Treasury,

809
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,830
but also every other male in Gu Mansion,

810
00:33:40,830 --> 00:33:41,590
not one missed,

811
00:33:41,590 --> 00:33:42,990
