812
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:46,720
You're using public office
to settle private scores.

813
00:33:47,510 --> 00:33:49,460
By order of the Grand Secretary.

814
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:51,370
Go ask him if you don't believe me.

815
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:05,180
[Eternal Glory]

816
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:32,710
Zhao!

817
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:34,670
Zhao!

818
00:34:37,110 --> 00:34:38,320
Ye Xian brought the constables
from the Penal Court

819
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,000
