820
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,230
They even want to arrest Rong.

821
00:34:40,230 --> 00:34:40,760
Hurry up!

822
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:42,880
Let's go check the front courtyard!

823
00:35:00,750 --> 00:35:02,960
I really don't know what's going on.

824
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:05,030
I am truly wronged!

825
00:35:05,510 --> 00:35:06,370
Your Highness,

826
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:08,600
