Take them away!

833
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:21,360
Move.

834
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,220
Your Highness!

835
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,710
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

836
00:35:23,710 --> 00:35:24,110
Move!

837
00:35:24,110 --> 00:35:25,150
You can't do this!

838
00:35:25,170 --> 00:35:26,840
-We're wronged!
-Your Highness!

839
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:28,320
-Uncle!
-Your Highness.

840
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:30,470
Uncle, why are you arresting me?

841
00:35:30,590 --> 00:35:31,110
-What exactly...
-Zhao!

842
00:35:31,110 --> 00:35:32,190
What exactly happened?

843
00:35:32,190 --> 00:35:32,960
Zhao!

844
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,780
Save me quickly, Zhao!

845
00:35:34,840 --> 00:35:35,770
Cousin Jinzhao!

846
