878
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:53,960
Mother!

879
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:54,800
Release Xian.

880
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,190
He's your nephew!

881
00:36:57,590 --> 00:36:58,110
Ye Xian!

882
00:36:58,840 --> 00:36:59,550
Ye Xian!

883
00:37:00,110 --> 00:37:01,370
-Fifth Auntie.
-Ye...

884
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:04,960
His Highness is only acting on orders.

885
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:06,670
