889
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,200
You are right.

890
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:14,960
Zhao.

891
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,660
It was my fault

892
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:19,090
