with the disaster relief grain.

901
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:33,510
He is in charge of
the Ministry of Revenue.

902
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:36,000
He'll have to be questioned
by the Three Judiciary Offices himself.

903
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,860
He will likely be imprisoned too.

904
00:37:39,390 --> 00:37:41,110
-Then what should we do?
-Mother.

905
00:37:41,110 --> 00:37:42,380
Then what should we do?

906
00:37:42,670 --> 00:37:43,860
All the men in our household

907
00:37:43,860 --> 00:37:44,990
have been arrested.

908
00:37:45,230 --> 00:37:46,230
What should we do?

909
00:37:46,550 --> 00:37:47,840
What should we do?

910
00:37:49,030 --> 00:37:50,030
What should we do?

911
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,640
Grandmother.

912
00:37:52,150 --> 00:37:53,880
It's not completely hopeless.

913
00:37:56,220 --> 00:37:57,440
Master's private seal,

914
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,570
letters,

915
00:37:58,760 --> 00:37:59,510
and account books...

916
00:37:59,510 --> 00:38:00,510
Find them all.

917
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:01,590
Don't miss anything.

918
00:38:01,590 --> 00:38:02,380
Be careful.

919
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:02,960
Yes.

920
00:38:06,030 --> 00:38:07,960
