the Ministry of Revenue at every step.

928
00:38:31,150 --> 00:38:32,670
[Wang Shenzhi, Chief Justice of the Imperial
Court of Judicial Review]

929
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,920
As Vice Minister of Revenue,

930
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:34,510
