931
00:38:34,510 --> 00:38:35,770
How could you not know?

932
00:38:36,500 --> 00:38:38,300
It was my momentary negligence.

933
00:38:38,670 --> 00:38:40,630
I didn't know the grain was replaced.

934
00:38:40,630 --> 00:38:41,960
Momentary negligence?

935
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:47,640
These two documents

936
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,350
were both approved by you

937
00:38:49,590 --> 00:38:51,800
half a month ago.

938
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:54,760
One of them, the grain replacement order,

939
00:38:55,070 --> 00:38:57,070
cites the reason that
the old grain stockpile,

940
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,420
[Censor Song Huai, Imperial Commissioner
for Relief Supervision]

941
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,440
if kept too long,

942
00:38:58,450 --> 00:38:59,130
[By imperial decree, funds from
the horse procurement treasury are hereby

943
00:38:58,710 --> 00:39:00,780
might spoil, harming both state granaries
and people's needs,

944
00:38:59,130 --> 00:38:59,820
allocated for the purchase of medicines.
Respect this imperial command]

945
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:02,420
so it requested new grain.

946
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:05,720
And the replacement order
and the grain allocation order

947
00:39:05,090 --> 00:39:07,510
[Chen Yanyun, Left Vice Minister
of Revenue, approved]

948
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:07,360
were only three days apart.

949
00:39:07,840 --> 00:39:08,510
How do you

950
00:39:09,150 --> 00:39:10,510
explain this?

951
00:39:17,210 --> 00:39:21,350
[Gu Dezhao, Director of the Treasury
of the Ministry of Revenue]

952
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,450
Zhao.

953
00:39:23,510 --> 00:39:24,190
This letter

954
00:39:24,190 --> 00:39:25,360
mentions this Sun Shitao,

955
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:26,440
in the 35th year of Jingning,

956
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,440
sought a transfer

957
00:39:27,510 --> 00:39:28,550
but was stopped by Master.

958
00:39:28,550 --> 00:39:29,230
So he poured tea

959
00:39:29,230 --> 00:39:32,090
on the memorial Master had just
finished drafting.

960
00:39:33,270 --> 00:39:34,640
[I serve as a junior clerk
assisting in this case]

961
00:39:34,660 --> 00:39:37,300
[Lest you be unaware of the hidden facts,
I humbly submit the truth of the matter]

962
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:38,630
It seems there's an old grudge.

963
00:39:38,630 --> 00:39:39,360
This is useful.

964
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:39,940
Keep it.

965
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:41,320
Okay.

966
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:42,880
Lord Chen.

967
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:45,060
Who in the Ministry of Revenue

968
00:39:45,190 --> 00:39:47,710
do you think has such great ability

969
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,970
to settle so many people and matters

970
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:53,670
