973
00:40:08,850 --> 00:40:09,650
I

974
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:12,800
have nothing to say.

975
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:14,380
Lord Chen,

976
00:40:15,030 --> 00:40:17,360
although you are an important minister
of the Imperial Court,

977
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:20,430
