985
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:17,960
How is it?

986
00:41:18,030 --> 00:41:18,960
Did you find out?

987
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:20,530
How is Third Master?

988
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:23,710
He's been locked up
in the Penal Court prison.

989
00:41:23,710 --> 00:41:25,710
They said he admitted to negligence.

990
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:26,840
The Three Judiciary Offices
held a joint trial,

991
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:28,240
and it was over in an hour.

992
00:41:31,190 --> 00:41:33,590
In this trap, I'm the pawn.

993
00:41:34,030 --> 00:41:35,430
Once the case breaks out,

994
00:41:35,710 --> 00:41:37,770
I'll inevitably face imprisonment.

995
00:41:38,510 --> 00:41:39,000
Zhao.

996
00:41:40,920 --> 00:41:41,510
Zhao.

997
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:43,320
I'm fine.

998
00:41:45,230 --> 00:41:46,320
So he took full responsibility

999
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:47,400
