1000
00:41:48,150 --> 00:41:48,710
Yes.

1001
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,030
Also,

1002
00:41:51,070 --> 00:41:52,800
I found a clue about Sun Shitao.

1003
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:55,120
I never expected.

1004
00:41:55,230 --> 00:41:55,670
Jiuheng

1005
00:41:55,460 --> 00:42:02,240
[A sage ruler attracts good ministers]

1006
00:41:55,670 --> 00:41:57,400
