1007
00:41:57,670 --> 00:41:59,090
He just said it was his own negligence

1008
00:41:59,090 --> 00:42:00,900
and took all the blame.

1009
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:04,360
He didn't defend himself,

1010
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:06,420
not because he didn't want to,

1011
00:42:06,510 --> 00:42:07,360
but because

1012
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:09,760
