1016
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:19,920
Yes,

1017
00:42:20,630 --> 00:42:22,020
Jiuheng is smart,

1018
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:24,440
but I also gave myself away on purpose,

1019
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:26,170
so he could play along.

1020
00:42:28,510 --> 00:42:30,110
You think I don't know?

1021
00:42:30,110 --> 00:42:31,310
You deliberately

1022
00:42:31,670 --> 00:42:33,000
kept him in the dark.

1023
00:42:34,110 --> 00:42:35,090
Prime Minister,

1024
00:42:35,440 --> 00:42:36,840
I had no choice.

1025
00:42:37,110 --> 00:42:38,230
With a matter this big,

1026
00:42:38,230 --> 00:42:41,090
the fewer people know at the beginning,
the better.

1027
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:42,150
Besides,

1028
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:43,840
Jiuheng

1029
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:45,150
may seem gentle on the outside,

1030
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:47,280
but he's extremely proud in his bones.

1031
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:49,600
I was afraid he would refuse

1032
00:42:49,670 --> 00:42:50,870
and ruin everything.

1033
00:42:51,190 --> 00:42:52,110
All right.

1034
00:42:52,110 --> 00:42:53,440
Let's not talk about this anymore.

1035
00:42:53,440 --> 00:42:55,150
When he gets out of prison,

1036
00:42:55,220 --> 00:42:56,840
I'll mediate

1037
00:42:56,860 --> 00:42:58,020
