1038
00:43:00,030 --> 00:43:01,300
How is Fan Chuan?

1039
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:03,030
He's sick.

1040
00:43:03,630 --> 00:43:05,760
He collapsed the day he returned home.

1041
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:06,920
Last night, when he heard Zhao Jichang

1042
00:43:06,920 --> 00:43:08,730
was found guilty of corruption, fraud,

1043
00:43:08,730 --> 00:43:10,480
reselling granary supplies,
and other crimes,

1044
00:43:10,480 --> 00:43:12,710
and ordered to be arrested
and escorted to the capital,

1045
00:43:12,710 --> 00:43:14,300
