1046
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:15,800
I was thinking

1047
00:43:15,800 --> 00:43:17,480
we can have those imperial censors,

1048
00:43:17,480 --> 00:43:18,510
such as Han Song, Wang Chuyi,

1049
00:43:18,510 --> 00:43:19,770
