1052
00:43:23,520 --> 00:43:28,500
[A sage ruler attracts good ministers]

1053
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:28,770
Prime Minister,

1054
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:29,730
The Governor of Shuntian Prefecture

1055
00:43:29,730 --> 00:43:31,460
