1062
00:43:41,030 --> 00:43:43,290
She wants to seek justice for her father.

1063
00:43:43,550 --> 00:43:44,970
Which Director Gu?

1064
00:43:45,510 --> 00:43:46,880
The Director of the Treasury,

1065
00:43:46,880 --> 00:43:47,730
Gu Dezhao.

1066
00:43:48,360 --> 00:43:50,230
The one who signed off
on the grain release.

1067
00:43:50,230 --> 00:43:51,880
His daughter?

1068
00:43:54,230 --> 00:43:55,150
The one

1069
00:43:56,550 --> 00:43:58,150
who competed

1070
00:43:58,150 --> 00:44:01,280
